{"word":"G1075 - γενεαλογέω - genealogéō - ghen-eh-al-og-eh'-o - Count by descent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">γενεαλογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">genealogéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ghen-eh-al-og-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Count by descent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வம்சவரிசைகளில் வா"},{"paragraph":"to act the genealogist"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1074 - γενεά - geneá - ghen-eh-ah'/1074\">G1074</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>reckon by generations</i>, that is, <i>trace in genealogy:</i> - count by descent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1074/1074\">G1074</a>, <a href=\"#/G1075/1075\">G1075</a>, <a href=\"#/G1076/1076\">G1076</a>, <a href=\"#/G35/35\">G35</a>"}]}